messages.content: I'm sure I'll be back in GR again before long. My number's 7346491650. Hope you're enjoying the research. Take care

I also no longer remember your  number (or most anyone elses' -_-) as I just got a new phone recently. However, if you ever come back to GR in the future, feel free to message me up.
